# Code Style

- Match existing module patterns: stdlib + numpy/psycopg2/pgvector only; no new dependencies.
- Keep functions focused; extract testable pure helpers for injection formatting and query building.
- Use `from __future__ import annotations`; type hints on public APIs.
- Secrets from env only (`KNOWWHERE_DB_URL`, `DEEPSEEK_API_KEY`); never hardcode.
- Log with `logging`, not print, in plugin code; no `/tmp` debug markers.
- Tests: unittest + mocks for unit; prefixed live PG fixtures with guaranteed cleanup for integration.
- German user-facing strings OK in docs; code/comments English unless mirroring existing files.
